The U.S. Agriculture Department forecast South Africa's 1986/87 corn crop 8.50 mln tonne v 9.50 mln tonne month. It estimate 1985/86 crop 8.08 mln v 8.08 mln month. USDA forecast South African 1986/87 corn export 2.10 mln tonne v 3.00 mln tonne month 1985/86 export 2.75 mln tonne v 2.75 mln tonne month. Reuter 